snippet.title: [DOAXVV] New Venus Release! Introducing Tina
snippet.description:
Tina, a character from the DOA series, has finally come to "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!" (Voice: Yuko Nagashima)
Enjoy a new vacation with the new Venus Tina, a superstar full of dreams who aims to be No. 1 in the Venus Festival in order to spread her name around the world.

○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/en/lp.html
○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam,Johren) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：Steam 10 April 2019 (Wednesday), Johren 1 July 2021 (Thursday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in Steam,Johren
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
